{"tid":1472603,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"《APEX LEGENDS》討論區 #10 無啦啦冇左個post","createTime":"2019-08-14T15:23:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T08:54:02.000Z","uid":126835,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"186231f89e5251ebd3e3ea0d1a10aa7d25e51281","tid":1472603,"uid":126835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:23:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.wccftech.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/apex-legends-keyart.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.wccftech.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F02%2Fapex-legends-keyart.jpg&h=deddba13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">前言</span></div></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">Apex Legend係EA旗下工作室Respawn Entertainment開發。之前嘅作品有Titanfall, Titanfall 2(當時為EA合作夥伴)。Apex Legend係屬於Titanfall嘅世界觀。<br />\n<br />\nRespawn Entertainment嘅核心成員，係由Activision旗下工作室Infinity Ward核心成員於2010年走出後成立(包括IW創辦人)。分裂前著名作品有COD, COD2, Modern Warfare &amp; Modern Warfare 2</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">遊戲簡介</span></div></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">3人組隊20隊互片 團隊合作最重要<br />\n有別於其他加入 Battle Royale(下稱:食雞模式) 的遊戲， APEX LEGENDS 並沒有常見的故事模式或單人模式，玩家可以和朋友或任何其他網上玩家組成3人 小隊進行遊戲，和遊戲中另外 20組 3人小隊( 合共 60 位玩家)進行大逃殺對戰。一如其他同類遊戲，手無寸鐵的玩家一開始需要由飛機跳下，選擇合適的地方盡快尋找武器及裝備。而在 APEX LEGENDS 中，遊戲會以 4 個回合的方式進行(每個回合 4 分鐘)，而地圖亦會不斷收窄令玩家更快遇見敵人，確保不會純粹在地圖上亂走大海撈針。</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">遊戲攻略</span></div></span></strong><br />\nPro Tips + Secrets from jackfrags<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hUYqneuuLOA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DhUYqneuuLOA&d=ldtyJnQDYvl76HjiXEXVXL3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=5dd13496\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hUYqneuuLOA</a><br />\n <br />\n<br />\nLoot Area<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q2gFb73.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq2gFb73.jpg&h=b3ccc56c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">New</span> Detailed Weapon Stat Chart<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qdgSWk3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqdgSWk3.png&h=a223b649&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nDrop<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hidNLex.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhidNLex.png&h=5c6c3111&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">遊戲精華</span></div></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n <a href=\"https://youtu.be/goCDWaG9mSM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FgoCDWaG9mSM&d=ldtyJnQDYvl76HjiXEXVXL3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=3472b31d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/goCDWaG9mSM</a><br />\n <br />\n<br />\nTwitch Rivals<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/Y2tphqr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY2tphqr.png&h=70bc96a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nNew Weapon - The Havoc Energy Rifle<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n <a href=\"https://youtu.be/1P7z-PLs8p0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F1P7z-PLs8p0&d=ldtyJnQDYvl76HjiXEXVXL3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=d15f684e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/1P7z-PLs8p0</a><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">即日起PC、PS4、XBOX ONE 平台上免費下載</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ea.com/zh-tw/games/apex-legends\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ea.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fgames%2Fapex-legends&d=ldtyJnQDYvl76HjiXEXVXL3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=80097dd1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ea.com/zh-tw/games/apex-legends</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">P.S. 暫時PC, PS4, XBOX並不支援跨平台對戰</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"d6c7e635b97514afdc5ca3029678c2c23bea60e3","tid":1472603,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:24:15.000Z","msg":"<code>風委會自動留名系統啟動，請勿負評干擾運作。</code>"},{"pid":"c2a4fb3431f5e61135f08abb2841dfc6e97f6d2e","tid":1472603,"uid":126835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6c7e635b97514afdc5ca3029678c2c23bea60e3","tid":1472603,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:24:15.000Z","msg":"<code>風委會自動留名系統啟動，請勿負評干擾運作。</code>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:26:45.000Z","msg":"唔該幫推"},{"pid":"7e47447fa64bb7cd1705761e32c4d1edffee5528","tid":1472603,"uid":11644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:27:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a47c079eba8d697dd2bcac9f7ef974d1f9b90eff","tid":1472603,"uid":126835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e47447fa64bb7cd1705761e32c4d1edffee5528","tid":1472603,"uid":11644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:27:08.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:27:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29f74086e84ba7c8e0bd8c30f8dc1abbdad98991","tid":1472603,"uid":65937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:32:35.000Z","msg":"舊post咩事被del<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> btw想買晒d新skin但好貴"},{"pid":"f49954022b71f56c1186b5ea38994a166f4c5654","tid":1472603,"uid":126835,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"29f74086e84ba7c8e0bd8c30f8dc1abbdad98991","tid":1472603,"uid":65937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T15:32:35.000Z","msg":"舊post咩事被del<img s